node.text:
On my latest podcast, I sat down with @DrWarrenFarrell, Ph.D.⁣
⁣
We discussed “The Boy Crisis”, parenting, the importance of parental dialogue and couples communication, delayed gratification, what is needed for children to do their best, the father’s catch-22, the disposable male crisis, and more.⁣
⁣
This episode is now live on YouTube, Apple Podcasts, and Spotify.

Click the link in my bio for more.
⁣
Recorded 05/25/2021.

⁣

⁣
This episode is now live on YouTube, Apple Podcasts, and Spotify.

Click the link in my bio for more.
⁣
Recorded 05/25/2021.

From my appearance on the "The Tim Ferris Show" - @TimFerriss⁣
⁣
